data.description: Step into modern luxury with this spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, located on the outskirts of Eau Claire in the Town of Union. Built in 2014, this contemporary gem is situated on a generous 1.5-acre corner lot. The heart of this home is the inviting open-concept living area. The chef's kitchen is a culinary haven, offering modern amenities, ample counter space, and a central island perfect for both cooking and casual dining. The living room offers a cozy retreat where you can relax and soak in the peaceful neighborhood ambiance. The lower level is complete with a walk out patio and lofty 9-foot ceilings that create a sense of spaciousness. This property also features a generously sized two-car garage for extra storage and to fit your cars and equipment. Experience the countryside while being just minutes away from the vibrant city of Eau Claire. Don't miss this unique opportunity to make this modern, spacious, and scenic home your own. Call today for a showing!
